	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Either use &quot;oe Necromancer_Audience&quot; in ReCon or go to the Audience route through the debugbook.&#xD;&#xA;- Escape or kill the cage you get teleported into.&#xD;&#xA;- Kill combat.&#xD;&#xA;- Go into the central corridor and to the Assault entrance of the Colony&#xD;&#xA;- Interact with S_COL_Entrance_Audience_Tentacle_c7291e48-45e1-43c5-b243-8b4716e1344e" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="11" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="An interaction with a huge tentacle that is psychically connected to the Elder Brain. Will only appear at the Colony's Moonrise Assault entrance if we came from the Necro-Lab - the tentacle won't have broken through Moonrise Tower. The tentacle will disappear again once the Elder Brain departs.&#xD;&#xA;A psionic pulse will emanate from the tentacle when we approach it, and we will get psychically told some personal history from the Elder Brain." />
			<children>
				<node id="defaultAttitudes">
